<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-47-0002 </DOCNO><TEXT>The document reproduces the text of the joint USSR-USA statement followingthe summit meeting between the President of the United States, RonaldW. Reagan and the General Secretary of the Central Committee of the CommunistParty of the Soviet Union, Mikhail S. Gorbachev, held in Moscow betweenMay 29 - June 2, 1988. It refers to the arms control (including nuclearweapons), human rights and humanitarian concerns, regional issues, bilateralaffairs and further meetings.</TEXT></DOC>